{"data":[{"date":"12:49 13/07","title":"N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 N\u1eef Myanmar (KT): Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u1ea1ng 3 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM 3-0 N\u1eee MYANMAR\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/175441-Highlight-Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Hai b\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng. \u01afu th\u1ebf h\u01a1i nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 10: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. S\u1ed1 7 Tuy\u1ebft Dung ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb lao v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-10.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 12: N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar th\u00ec s\u1ed1 23 Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ef3nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng dem v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-12.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 15: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1eeb s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng bay ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n trong gang t\u1ea5c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-15.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 19: S\u1ed1 8 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba n\u1eef Myanmar r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng song kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-19.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 22: N\u1eef Myanmar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1 ly xa n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 29: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. N\u1eef Myanmar c\u1ed1 t\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u00f2n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 31: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00fat v\u1ecdt x\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 36: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y sau c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u1eef Myanmar t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-38.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 41: Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, \u01b0u th\u1ebf n\u1eb1m trong tay tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Hi\u1ec7p 1 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat d\u00e0nh cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 Tuy\u1ebft Dung, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 47: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo v\u00e0o trong cho Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 54: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. N\u1eef Myanmar c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-53.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 58: Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-58.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 62: Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat g\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-62.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 69: C\u00c1CH BI\u1ec6T \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C GIA T\u0102NG. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb V\u00e2n v\u1eeba v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n solo \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-69.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 70: TR\u1eacN \u0110\u1ea4U AN B\u00c0I. Ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 1 ph\u00fat sau, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn v\u1edbi pha kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, x\u1eed l\u00fd g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-71.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 75: N\u1eef Myanmar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp trong khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 80: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong khi n\u1eef Myanmar c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 89: N\u1eef Myanmar kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m sao ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-88.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4194","checkdouble":"191100"},{"date":"14:54 13/07","title":"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/tuong-lai-gdkt-gede-sap-duoc-vff-dinh-doat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi G\u0110KT ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Jurgen Gede theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.</h2><h2>VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/19/Tuong-lai-GDKT-Jurgen-Gede-sap-duoc-VFF-dinh-doat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede l\u00e0m G\u0110KT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2016 theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. B\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng trong c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 &nbsp;VCK U20 World Cup, U15 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 qu\u00e2n VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a VFF. V\u00e0 sau 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u00f4ng Gede \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gede v\u00e0 VFF s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n trong th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, sau khi \u00f4ng Gede tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c &ldquo;ch\u1ed1t&rdquo; h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa G\u0110KT Gede v\u00e0 VFF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, G\u0110KT Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u1edbn trong 2 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0 VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4193","checkdouble":"191108"},{"date":"15:55 13/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u2018Messi Th\u00e1i Lan\u2019","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/3/nong-doi-bong-nhat-ban-chinh-thuc-mua-dut-messi-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Consadole Sapporo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Consadole Sapporo&nbsp;</span>ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Consadole Sapporo t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i.&nbsp;T\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Jay&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/them-cau-thu-thai-lan-ghi-ban-o-giai-jleague-1-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chanathip ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Consadole Sapporo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 1 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J1 League, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0&nbsp;ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho&nbsp;Consadole&nbsp;\u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa Consadole Sapporo v\u1edbi Consadole Sapporo, Chanathip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Consadole v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110N\u00c1 n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Muangthong United. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Muangthong United s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 570 ngh\u00ecn USD (13,1 t\u1ec9&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng) t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Chanathip. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Consadole Sapporo mua \u0111\u1ee9t, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J-League 1. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4192","checkdouble":"191109"},{"date":"14:52 13/07","title":"Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ecfng \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u01b0u ti\u00ean vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" title=\"tien ve NGolo Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Kante s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n Kante, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Blues ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb Leicester.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Barca-muon-mua-Kante-cua-Chelsea-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca c\u00f3 Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e3i l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Kante cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. HLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb Chelsea, Barca c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Mirror cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante-172-190952.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante</span>, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4191","checkdouble":"191104"},{"date":"16:35 13/07","title":"Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Vi\u1ec7c CR7 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd anh m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. Ngo\u00e0i ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, Juve c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho Ronaldo m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 khi \u1edf Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Real, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i khi ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t n\u1ed1t Gareth Bale. Sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd chia tay s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Real-muon-mua-Rodrigo-ve-thay-Ronaldo,-nguoi-moi-sang-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Jvuentus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, M.U t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Bale v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u00f2n Real, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Neymar, Kylian Mbappe r\u1ed3i Eden Hazard v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rodrigo l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Los Blancos v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" title=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo c\u1ee7a Valencia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRodrigo t\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Real m\u00f9a 2009/10 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi sang Benfica r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi Valencia nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui, \u00f4ng t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Rodrigo tr\u00ean \u0110T U21 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 trung phong l\u1eabn d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh. D\u00f9 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo hay Bale, Rodrigo \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nacho, Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Isco, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh \u1edf c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;sao b\u1ef1&rdquo; Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/cuu-sao-real-danh-gia-cao-ronaldo-hon-hazard-neymar-187-191072.html\">C\u1ef1u sao Real \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ronaldo h\u01a1n Hazard, Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard-180-191070.html\">Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi gi\u00e1 cao kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea-180-191016.html\">Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4190","checkdouble":"191111"},{"date":"12:00 13/07","title":"PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/9/psg-mu-va-chelsea-dai-chien-vi-bonucci.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Corriere dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin, PSG, Chelsea v\u00e0 MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci r\u1eddi AC Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Leonardo Bonucci</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, sau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Fred v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Dalot, Mourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG, Chelsea v\u00e0 MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Leonardo Bonucci r\u1eddi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG, Chelsea v\u00e0 MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Leonardo Bonucci r\u1eddi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/PSG,-Chelsea-va-MU-muon-dua-Leonardo-Bonucci-roi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-thu-3-cua-mu-tri-gia-37-trieu-bang-172-189941.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leonardo Bonucci c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</span>, Mourinho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Smalling ho\u1eb7c Jones \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Leonardo Bonucci r\u1eddi AC Milan, The Blues nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i thay David Luiz, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge. Vi\u1ec7c Gary Cahill kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh quan t\u00e2m Bunucci.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCorriere dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao, HLV Thomas Tuchel mu\u1ed1n PSG \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bunucci r\u1eddi AC Milan l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bonucci c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan t\u1eeb Juventus, anh \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 48 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/9/psg-mu-va-chelsea-dai-chien-vi-bonucci.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi AC Milan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBonucci r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi AC Milan, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. C\u0169ng theo Corriere dello Sport, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 song PSG, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBonucci l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Juventus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG, M.U ho\u1eb7c Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4189","checkdouble":"191094"},{"date":"12:15 13/07","title":"Tottenham l\u1ea1i \"g\u1ea1 g\u1eabm\" MU mua Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/tottenham-lai-ga-gam-mu-mua-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Yahoo Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alderweireld cho MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Davinson Sanchez khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Tottenham-ban-Toby-Alderweireld-cho-MU-voi-gia-55-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Spurs \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, song HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Tottenham c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Spurs \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u sao Atletico gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng khi\u1ebfn Tottenham bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Yahoo Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, MU \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ecfi mua Alderweireld nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 Spurs v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham l\u1ea1i g\u1ea1 g\u1eabm MU mua Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tottenham l\u1ea1i g\u1ea1 g\u1eabm MU mua Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/tottenham-lai-ga-gam-mu-mua-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 40 \u0111\u1ebfn 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Alderweireld mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Spurs th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989, n\u1ebfu M.U g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Phil Jones ho\u1eb7c Chris Smalling \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00f2i 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi kho\u1ea3ng 40 \u0111\u1ebfn 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Tottenham kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Man \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/toby-alderweireld-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dat-duoc-thao-thuan-voi-mu-172-188360.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alderweireld ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4188","checkdouble":"191095"},{"date":"14:31 13/07","title":"John Terry n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/john-terry-noi-gi-sau-khi-chelsea-sa-thai-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia cho The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chelsea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 The Blues c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Conte m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/John-Terry-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea xem x\u00e9t nghi\u00eam t\u00fac kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u00f4m qua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte</span> sau khi hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 9 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 Conte, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c HLV.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay Conte, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Napoli. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Terry c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia cho The Blues.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"John Terry phat bieu ve Conte\" title=\"John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Conte\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/john-terry-noi-gi-sau-khi-chelsea-sa-thai-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>John Terry ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i y\u00eau ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 Conte \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi, t\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Conte gi\u00fap t\u00f4i thu v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i th\u00edch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Conte, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Conte, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00fac \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia may m\u1eafn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. F4 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u00ec \u00f4ng m\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lopetegui tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4187","checkdouble":"191101"},{"date":"16:01 13/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Andreas Christensen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Napoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t t\u1ee9 3 Serie A (sau Juventus v\u00e0 Roma), h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/HLV-Maurizio-Sarri-toi-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede Napoli, Kalidou Koulibaly l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 95% \u1edf Serie A 2017/18.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Stamford Bridge, trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Conte s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChristensen c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 93,4%, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Koulibaly. N\u1ebfu HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Christensen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Manchester City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 35 v\u00e0 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-HLV-Sarri-dan-dat-Chelsea-thay-Conte-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri gi\u00fap Chelsea mua Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 b\u1edfi Jorginho \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 2 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Jorginho c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri. Theo ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Vi\u1ec7c Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea lo l\u1eafng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea song mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV 58 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea quanh Hazard, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Antonio Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Conte l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho Chelsea trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, theo \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" title=\"Chelsea thay conte sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/John-Terry-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 Conte \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu chung s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span>. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u1ee9 9 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Abramovich.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAn \u1ee7i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Conte l\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho c\u00e1c HLV.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/Thay-gi-sau-vu-tien-ve-Ross-Barkley-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y Ruben Loftus-Cheek l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Sarri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Diego Costa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata s\u1eafp b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Morata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. C\u1ef1u sao Real li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n tranh ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 Morata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Dries Mertens c\u1ee7a Napoli ho\u1eb7c Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Conte t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, song khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Morata \u1edf Stamford Bridge ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4186","checkdouble":"191110"},{"date":"16:58 13/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, vi\u1ec7c Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o: &quot;Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian Antonio Conte \u1edf c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, ch\u00fang ta gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 v\u00e0 FA Cup l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 8&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa thai HLV Antonio Conte truoc them mua giai moi.\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 30 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 38 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 13 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong Antonio Conte lu\u00f4n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>T\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c HLV Antonio Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. HLV Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m trong vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ru\u1ed3ng r\u1eaby Diego Costa.<br>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Conte?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf  n\u00f3ng \u1edf Stamford Bridge sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Conte l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3,  Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 59  tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Sarri ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli.  Trong ba m\u00f9a d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Naples gi\u00e0nh  scudetto nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m c\u1ea7u  th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y Antonio Conte ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi  \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft  th\u00fac, c\u00e1c HLV s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eb1m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho  m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 HLV Antonio Conte:</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/john-terry-noi-gi-sau-khi-chelsea-sa-thai-conte-172-191101.html\">John Terry n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri-172-191093.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sarri quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea &ldquo;ph\u1ee5 t\u00ecnh&rdquo; Conte?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen-172-191091.html\">T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, sao Chelsea kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vu-hlv-sarri-den-chelsea-co-dien-bien-moi-172-191036.html\">V\u1ee5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4185","checkdouble":"191114"},{"date":"10:17 13/07","title":"Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a AS Roma, Kevin Strootman t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u2018l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u2019 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus.</h2><h2>Kevin Strootman kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin Strootman\" title=\"Kevin Strootman\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2014/12/23/chuyen-nhuong-mua-dong-real-quyet-chien-man-utd-vi-strootman.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kevin Strootman t\u1ef1 tin khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Serie A</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c &lsquo;v\u1eaft chanh b\u1ecf v\u1ecf&rsquo; khi chia tay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i Cristiano Ronaldo sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. T\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, CR7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Seria A. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 cao tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o &lsquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rsquo; trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 AS Roma Kevin Strootman v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan s\u1ebd k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t Ronaldo khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Juventus trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c h\u00fat cho gi\u1ea3i Serie A. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec Ronaldo ch\u1eb3ng mang t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a Juve trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef su\u1ed1t 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/cuu-sao-real-danh-gia-cao-ronaldo-hon-hazard-neymar-187-191072.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/cuu-sao-real-danh-gia-cao-ronaldo-hon-hazard-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/cuu-sao-real-danh-gia-cao-ronaldo-hon-hazard-neymar-187-191072.html\">C\u1ef1u sao Real \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ronaldo h\u01a1n Hazard, Neymar</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi Michel Salgado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid kh\u00f3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/Ryan-Giggs-chia-se-ve-Ronaldo-Vi-Messi,-cau-ay-phai-toi-Juve-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4184","checkdouble":"191088"},{"date":"09:26 13/07","title":"Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Sau khi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Barca quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Willian</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nSky Sports m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. M\u1edbi tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh c\u01a1 quan truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngu\u1ed3n tin g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha chi ra t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 nhen nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp tr\u00f2n 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00eda Blaugrana g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1c b\u1ecf. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Barca n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u1ecfi mua Willian l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n chi tr\u1ea3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t chia tay 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho v\u00ec c\u00e1c l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u00e3 sang ch\u00e2u \u00c1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Paulinho\" title=\"tien ve Paulinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/chinh-thuc-tien-ve-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Paulinho \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Iniesta b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Vissel Kobe th\u00ec Paulinho l\u1ea1i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a CLB c\u0169 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Barca ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 cho ra m\u1eaft b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Arthur Melo. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Willian c\u1ee7a anh. B\u1ed9 ba x\u1ee9 Samba l\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho, Arthur v\u00e0 Willian h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn Barca th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-cu-nguoi-den-phap-dam-phan-mua-rabiot-180-190971.html\">Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang-180-190953.html\">Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-toi-la-liga-nhung-khong-phai-real-172-190865.html\">Eden Hazard t\u1edbi La Liga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/psg-chi-270-trieu-euro-mua-coutinho-180-190772.html\">C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4183","checkdouble":"191078"},{"date":"10:11 13/07","title":"Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n khi CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, anh l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u1ede \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo sau \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. CR7 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n khi CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Real Madrid. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho Real Madrid. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac Ronaldo m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft NHM Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Real v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Ronaldo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Modric kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn QBV 2018</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric phan phao truyen thong Anh sau khi DT Croatia gianh chien thang.\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau khi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Croatia v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB hay \u0110TQG th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4182","checkdouble":"191085"}]}